1. The US SEC applied to the court to withdraw the lawsuit against Binance;
2. Paris Saint-Germain Football Club announced that it has included Bitcoin in its financial reserves;
3. WalletConnect: Solana mobile phone will participate in the Solana ecosystem WCT token airdrop application plan;
4. Arthur Hayes: ETH may rise to US$5,000 before the end of the year, setting a new record high;
5. OpenSea: The OS2 platform ends the testing phase and is open to the public, and will airdrop SEA tokens;
6. The US SEC clarified that some PoS staking activities do not belong to securities transactions;
7. Tether CEO: The company holds more than 100,000 bitcoins and 50 tons of gold;
8. The Trump administration is considering a measure that allows tariffs of up to 15%, which will be valid for 150 days;
9. Placeholder Partner: The current market correction does not mean the end of the market, and the risk structure is still good;
10. Solana Ecological Token Issuance Platform Cooking.City Completed US$7 Million in Financing, Jump Crypto Lead investor;
11. Head of the US SEC Crypto Working Group: Crypto investors should be responsible for their own investment decisions instead of complaining to the government.
